name: Still Struggling for American Liberty
description: This image, "Still Struggling for American Liberty" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to depict the ongoing struggle for liberty for all in America. The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer.
